title: LilyMorgan1
body:
Lily: Hey! My name is Lily, I'm the VP. You're Lucy, right?

[[Yep!|101]]
[[Sure am!|101]]

Morgan: That's great to hear.
Lily: We're so happy to finally be meeting everyone properly, this season is always so exciting.
Lily: All of you guys seem so put together!
Lily: I was like freaking out when I joined Lambda Lambda, but you guys have your shit together.
Morgan: Yea, me too.

[[Thanks!|301]]
[[I can be overwhelming, haha.|302]]

Lily: Great to have you here! This is Morgan, the Treasurer.
Morgan: Hi. How are you doing?

[[I'm great!|201]]
[[I'm excited!|201]]

Lily: Well, not too overwhelming, I hope.
Lily: All pledges are encouraged to come to us with any worries or concerns, we're here for you.

[[Thank you!|301]]
[[You're the best.|301]]

Lily: Yes, of course.
Lily: Anyway, we have a surprise planned for after dinner, so make sure to tell everyone to not tuck in early if you see them going upstairs.
Lily: Sound good?

[[Yes!|401]]
[[Sounds great.|401]]

Lily: Awesome! I'll see you later then.

[[Okay, bye!|501]]
[[See you later!|501]]
